TY  - JOUR
T1  - Geographic Decomposition of the Shortest Path Problem, with an Application to the Traffic Assignment Problem
AU  - Lansdowne, Zachary F.
AU  - Robinson, David W.
Y1  - 1982/12/01
PY  - 1982
